These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, adventure, zombie, sports
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person watching western movies is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
5. the person watching western movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | western | adventure | sports | zombie |
| Pet        | dog | goat   | mouse | horse    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, rabbit, snake, fish
There are 4 different nationalities: french, german, nigerian, russian
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
2. the french is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
4. the french is the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the german is on the right of the nigerian##1
6. the french is the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Pet   | snake | goldfish  | rabbit  | fish |
| Nationality   | russian    | french | nigerian | german    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, pomegranate, watermelon
City: hamburg, paris, nizza, miami
1. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
2. the person eating pomegranate is in an even position##4
3. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
4. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pomegranate | grapes    | carrot      |
| City   | nizza        | miami     | hamburg | paris |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, reading, woodworking
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, watermelon, nectarine, spinach
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person eating cucumber and the person eating spinach##2
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person eating nectarine is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
5. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking | drawing | reading |
| Food   | nectarine       | cucumber   | watermelon    | spinach  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, paramedic, engineer, lawyer
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, indian, russian
1. the engineer is on the right of the russian##1
2. the australian is the lawyer##1
3. the indian is on the right of the musician##1
4. the paramedic is on the far left##1
5. the engineer is in an odd position##4
6. the american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Job   | paramedic  | musician    | engineer   | lawyer       |
| Nationality   | american | russian | indian | australian |

