.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, epic, time-travel
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, cooking, baking, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an even position##4
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | documentary | time-travel | animation |
| Hobby   | drawing | cooking     | writing  | baking  |

