.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, family, mystery, western
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, bartender, teacher, security-guard
1. the security-guard is in an odd position##4
2. the teacher is on the left of the photographer##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the security-guard is the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the photographer##3
6. the bartender is on the right of the photographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | western | mystery | family    |
| Job     | security-guard | teacher  | photographer     | bartender |

