.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, fanta, milk, 7up
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking fanta##2
6. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the fish is between the person drinking juice and the owner of the goat##2
8. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Beverage   | fanta | juice      | 7up | milk |
| Pet   | bird  | guinea-pig | fish    | goat            |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, mango, pepper, watermelon
House: townhouse, art-deco, colonial, craftsman
1. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
2. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating mango##1
3. the townhouse house is between the art-deco house and the person eating pepper##2
4. the townhouse house is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating pepper is the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | watermelon | mango   | cabbage | pepper |
| House    | craftsman     | art-deco | townhouse     | colonial  |

