.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, juice, soy-milk
House: victorian, gothic-revival, tower, palace
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the palace house##1
2. the victorian house is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the palace house is between the victorian house and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. the palace house is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| House   | tower | gothic-revival | palace        | victorian    |

