.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, horse, cat, goat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, sailing, goat-polo
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is goat-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is goat-polo is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
5. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet   | turtle   | goat   | horse      | cat      |
| Sport      | cycling | sailing | goat-polo | biathlon |

