.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, magic-tricks, reading, woodworking
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, entrepreneur, pilot, mechanic
1. the mechanic is the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the pilot is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the entrepreneur is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | board-games | reading    | woodworking |
| Job   | security-guard   | pilot  | mechanic | entrepreneur     |

