.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, chess, gardening, sudoku
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, mystery, zombie, family
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
3. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
5. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching family movies and the person watching zombie movies##2
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | sudoku   | gardening | board-games | chess    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | mystery  | family     | scientific |

