.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, milk, water
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, golf, soccer, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
3. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
7. the person who's sport is badminton is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | water | 7up    | milk       | fanta |
| Sport       | golf  | soccer | biathlon | badminton  |

