4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the indonesian##1
5. the american is on the right of the person drinking water##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | canadian | indonesian | american  | pakistani |
| Beverage     | hot-chocolate      | water       | 7up | soy-milk     |

